  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Give People with Mental Health Conditions a Voice</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The voices of people with mental health conditions are often silenced, and this must stop. She Writes Woman is empowering this marginalised group to find their voices and advocate for their own rights. This project will help amplify the voices of 40 million Nigerians living with mental health conditions by empowering them with knowledge and information of their disability and rights. Through mass media, we will embark on telling our own stories and be included in policy making in Nigeria.</narrative>
  </description>
